oing pandemic of coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19)}}\n{{Use British English Oxford spelling|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{bots|deny=RMCD bot}}\n{{Infobox pandemic\n| name            = 2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic\n| map1            = COVID-19 Outbreak World Map per Capita.svg{{!}}upright=1.5\n| legend1         = {{Center|Map of confirmed cases per capita {{as of|2020|4|11|lc=y}}}}\n<div style=\"padding-left:3em; padding-right:0; overflow:hidden;\">\n<div class=\"legend\" style=\"-webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;page-break-inside: avoid;break-inside: avoid-column\"><span class=\"legend-color\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:\n#710000; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;1,000+ confirmed cases per million</div>\n<div class=\"legend\" style=\"-webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;page-break-inside: avoid;break-inside: avoid-column\"><span class=\"legend-color\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:\n#ac0100; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;500\u20131,000 confirmed cases per million</div>\n<div class=\"legend\" style=\"-webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;page-break-inside: avoid;break-inside: avoid-column\"><span class=\"legend-color\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:\n#db3938; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;200\u2013500 confirmed cases per million</div>\n<div class=\"legend\" style=\"-webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;page-break-inside: avoid;break-inside: avoid-column\"><span class=\"legend-color\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:\n#f79898; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;50\u2013200 c